    "title": {
        "rendered": "Sticky Posts (Classic Editor)"
    },
    "content": {
        "rendered": "\n<p><strong>Sticky Posts</strong> is a feature that places a post at the top of the front page of posts, keeping it there until new sticky posts are published.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Note: Sticky Post is\u00a0<a href=\"https://core.trac.wordpress.org/ticket/12702\">only available for the built-in post type post</a>\u00a0and not for custom post types.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"> How to stick a post</h2>\n\n\n\n<ol class=\"wp-block-list\"><li>Select the post you want to stick from&nbsp;<strong>Administration Screens &gt; Posts &gt; All Posts</strong>. Or, create new post from&nbsp;<strong>Administration Screens &gt; Posts &gt; Add New</strong>.</li><li>Select&nbsp;<strong>Document</strong>&nbsp;tab of the right side bar.</li><li>Select&nbsp;<strong>Stick to the Front Page</strong>.</li><li></li></ol>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"264\" height=\"294\" src=\"https://wordpress.org/documentation/files/2019/01/sticky_posts_block.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-11054952\" /><figcaption>Stick to the Front Page option</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">How to stick a post in Classic Editor</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>If you are a user of WordPress Version 3.x or 4.x, or Classic Editor, then follow below steps:</p>\n\n\n\n<ol class=\"wp-block-list\"><li>Select the post you want to stick from <strong>Administration Screens &gt; Posts &gt; All Posts</strong>. Or, create new post from <strong>Administration Screens &gt; Posts &gt; Add New</strong>.</li><li>Click <strong>Edit</strong> of Visibility in the right side bar.</li><li>Select <strong>Stick this post to the front page</strong>.</li><li>Click <strong>OK</strong>.</li></ol>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><a href=\"https://i0.wp.com/wordpress.org/documentation/files/2018/11/Screen-Shot-2016-12-16-at-11.23.29-AM.png?fit=230%2C300&amp;ssl=1\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"285\" height=\"371\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/wordpress.org/documentation/files/2018/11/Screen-Shot-2016-12-16-at-11.23.29-AM.png?fit=230%2C300&amp;ssl=1\" alt=\"In the publish metabox changing visibility to public and clicking the &quot;Stick this post to the front page&quot; checkbox\" class=\"wp-image-10851357\" srcset=\"https://wordpress.org/documentation/files/2018/11/Screen-Shot-2016-12-16-at-11.23.29-AM.png 285w, https://wordpress.org/documentation/files/2018/11/Screen-Shot-2016-12-16-at-11.23.29-AM-230x300.png 230w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 285px) 100vw, 285px\" /></a><figcaption>Creating a sticky post</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p></p>\n",
        "protected": false
    },
